# Param: large_bounds_threshold | float | 10000 | Large Bounds Threshold | min=1 | step=100
# Param: check_mobility | bool | True | Check Non-Static Mesh Mobility
# Param: check_collision | bool | True | Check No Collision Components
# Param: collision_scope | enum | static_mesh_only | Collision Scope | options=static_mesh_only,all_primitives
# Param: report_style | enum | compact | Report Style | options=compact,detailed,qa,machine
# Param: qa_mode | bool | True | QA Mode For EditorBinder Test Scene
# Param: max_items_per_group | int | 12 | Max Items Per Group | min=1 | max=100 | step=1
